name: lumberjack
shortDescription: Lumberjack is a versatile Angular logging library, specifically designed to be extended and customized. It provides a few simple log drivers (logging mechanisms, transports, log drivers) out-of-the-box. It's easy to enable the built-in log drivers or create and use custom log drivers.
longDescription: Lumberjack is a versatile Angular logging library, specifically designed to be extended and customized. It provides a few simple log drivers (logging mechanisms, transports, log drivers) out-of-the-box. It's easy to enable the built-in log drivers or create and use custom log drivers.
